strings: Decode Granite Image Printer Driver (GIPD) stream into human readable
form. Granite Systems was acquired by Monotype Imaging.
A GIPD stream is the printer language used by some Lexmark
printers, such as the X500 and Dell printers, such as the 1125 MFP.
-d basename Basename of .pbm file for saving decompressed planes
-r basename Basename of .jbg file for saving raw planes
